## Common setup mistakes to check if it doesn't work

| Symptom | Likely cause |
|---|---|
| Tool import fails or schema shows "invalid" | YAML formatting error — validate against `acr-ops-assistant-config.md` exactly, indentation matters |
| Assistant responds but numbers look wrong or stale | The n8n workflow's destination sheet wasn't cleaned between test runs — check `Get row(s) in sheet`'s actual item count first, independent of Dify |
| Assistant says it can't access the data at all | Webhook and Custom Tool schema disagree on HTTP method (GET vs POST) — a URL that "works" in a browser isn't proof the integration works; check both sides explicitly |
| Assistant answer is generic/doesn't cite real numbers | The LLM node's context variable isn't actually wired to `{{#getOpsCaseData.text#}}`, or the tool node was renamed and the reference broke |

For the underlying schema, prompt text, and the exact API contract referenced throughout this guide, see [`acr-ops-assistant-config.md`](acr-ops-assistant-config.md).

